itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Jarred Taylor, Dan Hollaway welcome special guests Derek Weida and Charlie Classic live from a tiny studio near Area 51 where for some strange reason the audio came in and out to make Dan and Ross sound like they were in a spaceship.  We debated about even airing it, but it was so f**ked up we had to.  The quality of the sound can only be chalked up to electromagnetic waves or something. Good luck.
